# 📞 Phonebook App

A simple and responsive **Phonebook App** built using **HTML, CSS, and JavaScript**.  
This project allows users to **add, search, edit, and delete contacts** easily.

---

## 🚀 Features

- ➕ Add new contacts
- 🔍 Search contacts instantly
- ✏️ Edit existing contacts
- ❌ Delete contacts
- 💾 Save contacts using Local Storage
- 📱 Responsive design

---

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript (DOM Manipulation)
- Local Storage

---

